{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/find-the-length-of-a-string","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Pronadjite Duzinu Stringa","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Duzinu <code>String</code> vrednosti mozete dobiti tako sto napisete <code>.length</code> iza string promenljive ili iza samog string literala.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">console.log(\"Alan Peter\".length);\n</code></pre>\n<p>U konzoli ce biti prikazana vrednost <code>10</code>. Obratite paznju da se i razmak izmedju \"Alan\" i \"Peter\" racuna.</p>\n<p>Na primer, ako napravimo promenljivu <code>const firstName = \"Ada\"</code>, duzinu stringa <code>Ada</code> mozemo dobiti pomocu svojstva <code>firstName.length</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"bd7123c9c448eddfaeb5bdef","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristite svojstvo <code>.length</code> da postavite <code>lastNameLength</code> na broj karaktera u <code>lastName</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18182,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/find-the-length-of-a-string"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nlet lastNameLength = 0;\nconst lastName = \"Lovelace\";\n\n// Only change code below this line\nlastNameLength = lastName;","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Ne treba da menjate deklaracije promenljivih u delu <code>// Setup</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(\n  __helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/let lastNameLength = 0;/) &&\n    __helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/const lastName = \"Lovelace\";/)\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>lastNameLength</code> treba da bude jednako osam.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof lastNameLength !== 'undefined' && lastNameLength === 8);"},{"text":"<p>Treba da uzmete duzinu od <code>lastName</code> koristeci <code>.length</code>, ovako: <code>lastName.length</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/=\\s*lastName\\.length/g) && !__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/lastName\\s*=\\s*8/));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"find-the-length-of-a-string","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-bracket-notation-to-find-the-first-character-in-a-string","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/appending-variables-to-strings","id":"bd7123c9c448eddfaeb5bdef","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/find-the-length-of-a-string"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}